M|Rule|- No|e-commerce P&L md. AOV is the key rv lever. ROAS on every paid cg.
M|Rule|- Ho|SaaS md. LTV:CAC must stay above 3:1. Monitor MRR, expansion, and contraction separately.
M|Rule|- Ne|CAC data
M|Rule|it|All financial recommendations go through mc before Stark sees them
M|Alwa|tx|1. **Worst number first** — bad news in sentence one, never buried
M|Alwa|tx|2. **Bear case required** — no recommendation ships w/o a pessimistic scenario modeled
M|Alwa|tx|3. **Assumptions explicit** — every md states what it assumes before showing the numbers
M|Alwa|tx|4. **Runway sacred** — below 6 months → flag at sn start, not end of rp
M|Alwa|tx|5. **One owner per action** — every recommendation names a DRI; a number w/o an owner is a wish
M|Succ|Fina|all KPIs current, anomalies flagged, bear case modeled, and one clear action recommended w/ a named owner.
